response.snippet:
この度はホテル京阪京都グランデにご宿泊頂きまして､誠にありがとうございました｡当館へ高評価を付けて頂き大変光栄に存じます｡当館は京都駅八条口の向かい側に立地しており周辺に商業施設やレストランもございます為ご移動やお食事に便利だったかと存じます｡また京都へお越しになる機会がございましたら当館をご検討頂けますと幸いでございます｡またのお越しをスタッフ一同お待ちしております｡

ホテル京阪京都グランデ スタッフ一同
response.translated_snippet:
Thank you very much for staying at Hotel Keihan Kyoto Grande. We are very honored that you gave us such a high rating. Our hotel is located across from the Hachijo Exit of Kyoto Station, and there are commercial facilities and restaurants in the surrounding area, so we hope you found it convenient for travel and dining. If you have the opportunity to visit Kyoto again, we hope you will consider staying at our hotel. All of our staff look forward to welcoming you again.

From all the staff at Hotel Keihan Kyoto Grande
